tourBios.carHigh: Made six cuts in nine starts in 2011, finishing a solo eighth at the Desert Dunes Classic. Finished T39 at the 2010 Riviera Nayarit Classic. Closed the 2008 season with a 64-65 start at Seaforth, ended up T53. In 2007, he collected a pair of top 10s at the Ford Culiacan Open (T10) and the Free Manitoba Press Classic (T9). Finished the Free Press Manitoba Classic shooting a final round 64 and closed with a 66 at Ford Culiacan Open. Played in the 2002 Air Canada Championship.
tourBios.otherInfo: Won five collegiate titles while at the College of the Desert.
tourBios.prYrSeason: Made four cuts in 2012, including a season-best T4 finish at the TOUR Championship.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Canada was T4th in 2012 at the Canadian Tour Championship.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T87th in Scoring Average (Actual) on the PGA TOUR Canada.
